    <h3>Spiral Mixer (Dough Mixer)</h3>
    <p>A spiral mixer is designed specifically for dough. The spiral hook stays in a fixed position while the bowl rotates, developing gluten quickly without overheating the dough. If you bake bread, roti, pizza dough, or any yeast-based product in volume, a spiral mixer is your primary bakery machine.</p>

