    <h3>Dough Kneader</h3>
    <p>A dough kneader is a simpler, more affordable alternative to a spiral mixer. It uses a single arm to knead dough in a horizontal tub. While it lacks the precision of a spiral mixer, a dough kneader is a popular bakery machine in India for small neighbourhood bakeries and sweet shops (mithai dukaan) where budget is tight.</p>
