    <h2 id="packaging">Packaging Machines — Wrapping, Sealing & Labelling</h2>

    <p>Packaging is often an afterthought for new bakery owners, but it directly impacts shelf life, food safety, and brand perception. Investing in the right packaging bakery machine saves time and makes your products look professional. Here are the current prices.</p>

