    <!-- SECTION 12: BAKERY KA SAMAN -->
    <!-- ============================================ -->
    <h2 id="bakery-ka-saman">Bakery Ka Saman — Hindi-English Guide for Beginners</h2>

    <p>Agar aap pehli baar bakery shuru kar rahe hain aur "bakery ka saman" search kar rahe hain, toh yeh section aapke liye hai. Hum yahan simple Hindi-English mein samjhayenge ki kya-kya chahiye aur kahan se khareedein.</p>

    <h3>Bakery Ka Saman — Complete List (Hindi Mein)</h3>
    <p>Bakery ka saman basically teen categories mein aata hai:</p>

    <p><strong>1. Bade Machines (Heavy Equipment):</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Oven (Bhatti):</strong> Sabse zaroori machine. Chhoti bakery ke liye convection oven (₹45,000 se shuru), badi bakery ke liye deck oven ya rotary oven.</li>
      <li><strong>Mixer (Aata Gundhne Ki Machine):</strong> Planetary mixer cake ke liye (₹12,000 se), spiral mixer bread ke liye (₹45,000 se).</li>
      <li><strong>Proofer (Khameer Uthane Ka Cabinet):</strong> Bread aur bun ke liye zaroori. ₹40,000 se shuru.</li>
      <li><strong>Display Counter (Dikhane Ka Counter):</strong> Customers ko products dikhane ke liye. ₹15,000 se shuru.</li>
      <li><strong>Fridge (Thanda Rakhne Ki Machine):</strong> Cream, butter, eggs rakhne ke liye. ₹25,000 se shuru.</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>2. Chhote Tools (Small Equipment):</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Trays (Pareeyaan):</strong> Baking ke liye aluminium trays. ₹150 per tray.</li>
      <li><strong>Moulds (Saanche):</strong> Cake, muffin, bread ke shapes ke liye. ₹300 se shuru.</li>
      <li><strong>Piping Bags (Cream Lagane Ka Bag):</strong> Cake decoration ke liye. ₹150 se set milta hai.</li>
      <li><strong>Tarazu (Weighing Scale):</strong> Saman tolne ke liye digital scale. ₹800 se shuru.</li>
      <li><strong>Thermometer (Tapman Naapne Ka):</strong> Oven aur bread ka temperature check karne ke liye. ₹300 se.</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>3. Packaging Ka Saman:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Sealer Machine:</strong> Packet band karne ke liye. ₹1,500 se shuru.</li>
      <li><strong>Labels aur Printer:</strong> FSSAI ke rule ke hisaab se label lagana zaroori hai. ₹5,000 se.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Bakery Ka Saman Kahan Se Khareedein?</h3>
    <p>India mein bakery ka saman khareedne ke kai tarike hain:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Online Marketplaces:</strong> BakeDesk.in (yahan aap verified dealers se directly baat kar sakte hain), IndiaMART, TradeIndia</li>
      <li><strong>Local Dealers:</strong> Har bade shehar mein commercial kitchen equipment ki market hoti hai — Delhi mein Chandni Chowk, Mumbai mein Lohar Chawl, Chennai mein Parrys</li>
      <li><strong>Factory Direct:</strong> Kuch manufacturers seedha bechte hain — isse best price milta hai</li>
      <li><strong>Used Equipment:</strong> Budget tight hai toh second-hand saman bhi option hai</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Agar aapko guidance chahiye, toh BakeDesk ki team se baat karein — hum aapke budget aur menu ke hisaab se exact list bana ke denge. Hamari <a href="/blog/how-to-buy-bakery-equipment">buying guide</a> bhi padh sakte hain.</p>

